{"tid":1471204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪想輸？宣傳818！","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T05:02:19.000Z","uid":132195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d7126b1b8e4e0761cf043da42fcc68c142f06675","tid":1471204,"uid":132195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:13:40.000Z","msg":"機場件事唔發生都發生咗，要點拆要檢討已經好多post，但係只係不斷回顧過去係冇用架！我哋仲要思考下一步點做，點樣可以壯大聲勢！而家成個熱門都冇人講818，星期日就係㗎啦！到時好似各區遊行得10幾20萬人行係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔夠</span></span></strong>架！<br />\n<br />\n唔該文宣手足、街站手足、AirDrop手足，甚至機場手足，都要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大大力宣傳818大遊行</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">818要晒佢冷</span></strong></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVwP2Mj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVwP2Mj.jpg&h=a4ad0aca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ye9ibEF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fye9ibEF.jpg&h=0ea76cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbBXsc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbBXsc1.jpg&h=63a34ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2Tu2Mo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2Tu2Mo.jpg&h=5df2770e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NPn0pZK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNPn0pZK.jpg&h=5add4519&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOLYbEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOLYbEO.jpg&h=13194594&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dc3b6cfa18a9f3638d46224dcdd79240debaaf0","tid":1471204,"uid":132195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T